#

Creamy Spinach and Ricotta Stuffed Shells

$15.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh-ProteinComfort Food

Tags:

PastaBakedItalianComfort Food

Description

Delicious pasta shells filled with creamy ricotta and fresh spinach, topped with marinara sauce and baked to perfection.

Ingredients

  • Jumbo pasta shells: 12 pieces
  • Ricotta cheese: 1 cup
  • Fresh spinach: 2 cups
  • Marinara sauce: 2 cups
  • Mozzarella cheese: 1 cup
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup
  • Garlic: 2 cloves
  • Olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
